lass=m><span class=title> ...</span><hr size=1> Velious has only been out a few days... and I know of at least 2 other places spells drop. Also, only two Wizard spells drop off GW's that I'm aware of -- Okiel's and Wakening Portal. Go explore <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uiueelyen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Iueelyen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/11/00 8:51:43 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> I got to camp them for 1 hour</span><hr size=1> Your right everyone is camping these 2 guys every day all day.  We waited out in the hall for 3 hours killing wurms until someone announced the camp was free.  And even then we had a higher level wizard get there before us and claim it.  We had to share spawns (I don't thing he was to happy about it but did it to keep the peace). We were able to loot:<br>SK spell (Shroud of hate)<br>Pally Spell <br>Bard Song <br>Shaman Spell (Blast of Poison)<br>2 wiz spells (Enticement of flame &amp; Wakening Lands port)<br><br>I never saw O'Keils drop.  This spell can be purchased from several vendors tho.  One being the first Igloo you see when you get off the boat.<br><br>Iuee<br><br><br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umagosian.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Magosian</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/11/00 12:08:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: this sucks</span><hr size=1> There are many other places the same spells drop.<br><br>So far we have found spells in:<br><br>Velketor's Labrynth (Wakening Lands Portal, Ice Spear of Solist (off of Velketor, 2 copies) along with some other class spells and bard songs)<br><br>Icewell Keep<br><br>Shardwurms in Great Divide<br><br>Necropolis<br><br>Cobalt Scar<br><br>Wakening Lands<br><br>Iceclad (from some high level turtle)<br><br>Plane of Growth (from any random mob)<br><br>I'm sure spells drop in other places too. I think it's somewhat like Kunark with a little twist. Certain level mobs drop certain level spells. But you won't find any level 60 spells from anything lower than level 60 (just like kunark). Anything higher COULD drop a lower level spell, but not higher. Just my thoughts.<br><br>Magosian<br>60 Sorcerer<br>Legacy of Steel<br>The Nameless <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umagosian.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Magosian</A> at: 12/11/00 12:10:11 pm<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showPrevMessage?topicID=5.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showNextMessage?topicID=5.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.emailToFriend?topicID=5.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This